				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					D&amp;D 5e - Fantasy Grounds
				</h2>
				

						
							
							
							
						
						
				<div class="content ">
					<div id="post_message_1848062">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							So WOTC is officially pushing this tool for D&amp;D now:<br />
<br />
<a href="https://www.fantasygrounds.com/buyFG/DungeonsAndDragons.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">https://www.fantasygrounds.com/buyFG...ndDragons.html</a><br />
<br />
I searched this forum for any references to FantasyGrounds and only came up with a thread on a game session Dmitry ran in 2008. <br />
<br />
